    "about_this_item": "<div class=\"dm-tabs__rte\" style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent; color:#2a211b; font-family:inherit;\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid; gap:16px; margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:16px 18px; border-radius:16px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.055); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10);\">\n      <div style=\"margin:0 0 6px; color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; line-height:1; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase;\">\n        Nature-Inspired Bedroom Statement\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n        Create a warm and restful bedroom with a rustic solid wood platform bed featuring a sculptural tree branch headboard, grounded proportions, and organic character.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">01</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Sculptural Tree Branch Headboard\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          Flowing branch-inspired lines create a dramatic focal point while bringing the natural movement and warmth of organic forms into the bedroom.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">02</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Grounded Low-Profile Platform\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          The substantial platform base gives the bed a calm, grounded presence while keeping the overall silhouette clean, balanced, and easy to style.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">03</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Warm Solid Wood Character\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          Natural wood tones and a matte finish give the frame a warm, substantial appearance suited to relaxed and design-focused interiors.\n        </p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; margin:0; padding:0;\">\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Rustic</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Organic Modern</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Cabin</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Boho</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.13); color:#5a3218; font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Wabi-Sabi</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">04</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Multiple Bedroom Size Options\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          Available size selections make it easier to choose a configuration for full, queen, king, or larger custom bedroom layouts.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">05</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Easy to Style With Natural Palettes\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          The natural wood tone pairs comfortably with soft neutrals and earthy colors, helping you create a calm and layered bedroom retreat.\n        </p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; margin:0; padding:0;\">\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Beige</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Cream</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">White</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.10); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.78); font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Sage</span>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex; padding:6px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.13); color:#5a3218; font-size:12px; line-height:1;\">Charcoal</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">06</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Designed for Cozy Interiors\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          A distinctive centerpiece for primary bedrooms, guest rooms, vacation homes, mountain cabins, boutique rentals, and other welcoming spaces.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:34px 1fr; gap:14px; padding:0 0 16px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.14); background:transparent;\">\n      <span style=\"width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:999px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.09); color:#5a3218; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.04em; line-height:1;\">07</span>\n      <div style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background:transparent;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 7px; padding:0; color:#1f1712; font-family:var(--font-heading-family, Georgia, serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.35; font-weight:500;\">\n          Statement Furniture With Organic Character\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:0; padding:0; color:rgba(42,33,27,0.76); font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; font-weight:400;\">\n          More than a place to sleep, the sweeping branch-style headboard gives the room visual movement and a custom, handcrafted-inspired presence.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"margin:2px 0 0; padding:13px 15px; border-radius:14px; background:rgba(91,50,24,0.06); color:rgba(42,33,27,0.72); font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; border:1px solid rgba(92,58,35,0.08);\">\n      Natural wood tone, grain appearance, and organic branch details may vary slightly, giving each finished bed its own individual character.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
